{
  "stem": "26609.10",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She quarreled later with me that I have money but didn't want to give it to her, the woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I said I didn't have-- that what I have looked through, I haven't got.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That what I-- and I kept it for her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I said, you give to your children too, and she has nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'll tell you later about her too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And as I went out, I didn't even say goodbye to her, nothing to my child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I didn't say where I'm going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, I'll come back soon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They rounded up on the-- the Gestapo rounded up-- they looked for a black market.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was illegal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there were people coming from the country selling a little bit of milk or a bit of butter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was illegal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the Germans surrounded us all and took us to prison for that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was-- first, not to the prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I'll tell you something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They rounded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was amongst them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I never went back to the child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "From there, they took us to a Ukraine militsiya.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was like a police not far from where I lived there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They called it militsiya, Ukraine militsiya.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They took us to the-- they rounded up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there were, I would say, about 80 to 100 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "There they started to question us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was like-- all the time, I was dressed poorly, like all the others.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't different from other country people like them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a skirt around and a blouse on like them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, we stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started to question us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where did you come from?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so they asked all others until they came to me-- two militsiya men, Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were worse than the Gestapo, much worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
